# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Un-ignore React source-tree files that CRA needs for cold-clone builds.
# These negations MUST stay after the blanket *.png/*.jpg/*.json excludes
# above. Without them tsconfig.json, package-lock.json, and public-tree
# assets (ort-wasm-*, favicon, images) get stripped from fresh clones and
# `npm run build` dies with "Module not found". See /CLAUDE.md for the
# full cold-clone build contract.
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
!doseedo-react/tsconfig.json
!doseedo-react/package-lock.json
!doseedo-react/public/
!doseedo-react/public/**
!doseedo-react/src/assets/
!doseedo-react/src/assets/**